    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint still holds a deep shine, though you will notice some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches from normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster and all electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a reliable and attractive choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
